Package: accessibility
Title: Calculating accessibility to amenities
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: c(
      person("Xavier", "Timbeau", email = "xavier.timbeau@sciencespo.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Maxime", "Parodi", email = "maxime.parodi@sciencespo.fr", role = c("aut")))
Description: The package is a wrapper of a routing system to calculate accessibility. It creates chunks of positions and amenities to manage the calculations and do parallel computations.
